msgstr "Geen QSOs gevonden die aan de criteria voor deze award voldoen!"

#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:18
#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:24
msgid "WAE Award"
msgstr "WAE Award"

#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:19
#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:25
msgid ""
"The oldest and most renowned of all DARC certificates is awarded for "
"contacts with amateur radio stations in European countries and on islands "
"listed in the WAE country list on different bands."
msgstr ""
"Het oudste en meest gerenommeerde van alle DARC-certificaten wordt toegekend "
"voor contacten met amateurradiostations in Europese landen en op eilanden "
"die vermeld staan op de WAE-landenlijst op verschillende banden."

#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:20
#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:26
msgid ""
"The WAE will be issued in the following modes: CW, SSB, Phone, RTTY, FT8, "
"Digital and Mixed Modes. It is issued in five classes: WAE III, WAE II, WAE "
"I, WAE TOP and the WAE Trophy."
msgstr ""
"De WAE wordt uitgegeven in de volgende modi: CW, SSB, Phone, RTTY, FT8, "
"Digitale en Gemengde modi. Het wordt uitgegeven in vijf klassen: WAE III, "
"WAE II, WAE I, WAE TOP en de WAE Trofee."

#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:22
#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:28
msgid "Fields taken for this Award: Region, DXCC"
msgstr "Velden voor deze Award: Regio, DXCC"

#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:201
#: application/views/awards/wae/index.php:215
msgid "WAE Name"
msgstr "WAE Naam"

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:8
msgid "WAIP Award"
msgstr "WAIP Award"

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:9
msgid ""
"The WAIP (Worked All Italian Provinces) Award is issued for contacts with "
"stations operating from Italian provinces. Italy has over 100 provinces, "
"making this a challenging and prestigious award."
msgstr ""
"De WAIP (Worked All Italian Provinces) Award wordt uitgegeven voor contacten "
"met stations die opereren vanuit Italiaanse provincies. Italië heeft meer "
"dan 100 provincies, wat dit een uitdagende en prestigieuze onderscheiding "
"maakt."

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:10
msgid ""
"Award categories: PHONE (SSB/AM/FM/SSTV), CW, DIGI (RTTY/PSK/FT8/etc.), and "
"individual bands. All provinces must be confirmed via QSL card. "
"Requirements: COL_STATE (2-letter province code), COL_DXCC=248 (Italy) or "
"225 (Sardinia), QSL card confirmation only. No satellite contacts allowed."
msgstr ""
"Award categorieën: PHONE (SSB/AM/FM/SSTV), CW, DIGI (RTTY/PSK/FT8/etc.), en "
"individuele banden. Alle provincies moeten bevestigd zijn via QSL-kaart. "
"Vereisten: COL_STATE (2-letterige provinciecode), COL_DXCC=248 (Italië) of "
"225 (Sardinië), alleen QSL-kaartbevestiging. Geen satellietcontacten "
"toegestaan."

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:11
msgid ""
"Province codes are 2-letter abbreviations (e.g., RM=Roma, MI=Milano, "
"NA=Napoli). See Italian provincial award references for complete list."
msgstr ""
"Provinciecodes zijn 2-letterige afkortingen (bijv. RM=Rome, MI=Milaan, "
"NA=Napels). Zie Italiaanse provinciale awardreferenties voor de volledige "
"lijst."

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:12
#, php-format
msgid "For more information about the WAIP award, visit: %s"
msgstr "Voor meer informatie over de WAIP-award, bezoek: %s"

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:12
msgid "WAIP Award Information"
msgstr "WAIP Awardinformatie"

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:23
msgid ""
"This award tracks worked and confirmed status for Italian provinces. Only "
"QSL card confirmations are accepted. Green = Confirmed, Orange = Worked but "
"not confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Deze prijs houdt de gewerkte en bevestigde status bij voor Italiaanse "
"provincies. Alleen QSL-kaartbevestigingen worden geaccepteerd. Groen = "
"Bevestigd, Oranje = Gewerkt maar niet bevestigd."

#: application/views/awards/waip/index.php:34
msgid "Progress towards working all Italian provinces:"
msgstr "Voortgang naar het werken in alle Italiaanse provincies:"

